1
00:00:32,150 --> 00:00:33,750
Something is wrong with you.

2
00:00:34,860 --> 00:00:35,780
You said it yourself.

3
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:37,140
Whenever we meet,

4
00:00:37,270 --> 00:00:38,950
we must not wait with our backs turned.

5
00:00:38,950 --> 00:00:40,460
We need to clearly see who is coming,

6
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:43,460
if their condition is right,
and if they brought anyone.

7
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:44,100
Yao.

8
00:00:44,910 --> 00:00:46,040
You broke the rules.

9
00:00:48,030 --> 00:00:48,860
I was wrong.

10
00:00:58,630 --> 00:00:59,070
Here.

11
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:02,080
The backup
of Hengyun Logistics' latest ledger.

12
00:01:07,710 --> 00:01:08,840
What's on your mind?

13
00:01:10,630 --> 00:01:11,550
I came early

14
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:13,630
and caught the sunrise.

15
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:16,640
The morning sun rising in the east—

16
00:01:16,860 --> 00:01:18,660
I haven't seen it for a long time.

17
00:01:21,660 --> 00:01:22,550
My son's name

18
00:01:22,990 --> 00:01:23,990
is Xudong.

19
00:01:25,470 --> 00:01:26,350
Yao Xudong.

20
00:01:27,300 --> 00:01:28,910
Since when do you have a son?

21
00:01:30,380 --> 00:01:31,710
Eight years ago today,

22
00:01:32,910 --> 00:01:34,370
he died in the line of duty.

23
00:01:38,470 --> 00:01:39,550
He...

24
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:41,110
was also a cop?

25
00:01:41,990 --> 00:01:42,920
A narcotics cop.

26
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:46,229
He was killed by drug traffickers?

27
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,710
He was tortured alive for 40 hours,

28
00:01:52,220 --> 00:01:53,680
wide awake the whole time,

29
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,350
right until the end.

30
00:01:58,990 --> 00:02:00,830
By the time the police found him,

31
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,140
his skull

32
00:02:02,630 --> 00:02:03,710
had been smashed,

33
00:02:04,990 --> 00:02:07,190
the skin on his legs had been peeled off,

34
00:02:07,910 --> 00:02:10,639
and there wasn't a single intact spot
on his body.

35
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:13,270
I've never told anyone about it.

36
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:16,890
We even used a pseudonym on his obituary.

37
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:21,100
He was an undercover too?

38
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:23,829
You know what?

39
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:27,750
Before his last mission,

40
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:29,870
he actually called me.

41
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:34,070
He wanted me to get him

42
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:37,660
one of those little cyanide capsules.

43
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,960
He said the mission was dangerous

44
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:43,520
and wanted to hide it in his tooth.

45
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:47,160
In case he couldn't hold out...

46
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:51,010
it might come in handy.

47
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:57,100
I...

48
00:02:57,540 --> 00:02:58,590
scolded him.

49
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:09,510
Maybe...

50
00:03:10,820 --> 00:03:11,750
Maybe...

51
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:14,670
I should have gotten it for him.

52
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,920
I should have done that for him.

53
00:03:25,350 --> 00:03:26,030
Yao,

54
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:28,890
when this mission is over,

55
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:30,590
I'll be your godson.

56
00:03:31,540 --> 00:03:32,430
Come on.

57
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:40,420
Communist Party members don't do that.

58
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:44,430
Then I'll go pay respect to him with you.

59
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,260
Well...

60
00:03:45,260 --> 00:03:46,430
Where is he?

61
00:03:46,820 --> 00:03:47,540
Yunnan.

62
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:49,260
Okay.

63
00:03:49,750 --> 00:03:51,210
I'll go to Yunnan with you.

64
00:03:58,430 --> 00:03:59,160
Jiang Cheng.

65
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:02,550
The reason I'm telling you this

66
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:05,500
is to let you know

67
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:08,380
that the path you've chosen

68
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:11,820
is really hard.

69
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:15,430
No matter how prepared you are,

70
00:04:17,670 --> 00:04:19,940
reality might be much more dangerous.

71
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,310
No matter how hard

72
00:04:24,900 --> 00:04:25,960
or dangerous it is,

73
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:27,600
I accept it.

74
00:06:40,810 --> 00:06:46,430
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

75
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:49,170
[Episode 22]

76
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:51,960
From your perspective,

77
00:06:52,260 --> 00:06:53,860
why did you refuse to answer?

78
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,820
Because you cared about his feelings.

79
00:06:57,820 --> 00:06:59,430
You were afraid of breaking his heart.

80
00:06:59,430 --> 00:07:00,560
What does that mean?

81
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:02,750
It means

82
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:06,960
you've fallen in love with him.

83
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:26,380
But it seems I've messed everything up.

84
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:33,500
It's not that complicated.

85
00:07:33,550 --> 00:07:35,190
As long as the love is still there,

86
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,650
everything can be solved.

87
00:07:37,310 --> 00:07:38,570
Besides, it looks to me

88
00:07:38,580 --> 00:07:39,580
like Professor Jiang

89
00:07:39,580 --> 00:07:41,070
is more or less a hopeless romantic.

90
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,470
He's very easy to handle.

91
00:07:44,580 --> 00:07:46,310
But you have to be careful.

92
00:07:46,990 --> 00:07:48,900
Professor Jiang is really outstanding.

93
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:50,140
Everyone around us

94
00:07:50,260 --> 00:07:52,700
treats him like a treasure, right?

95
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:54,670
When the Provincial Bureau leaders
came here,

96
00:07:54,670 --> 00:07:57,260
they wanted to poach him
as soon as they saw him.

97
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:59,520
Why does Professor Jiang come to our unit

98
00:07:59,670 --> 00:08:00,310
every now and then?

99
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:02,840
Could it be that he's interested
in Chief Tan?

100
00:08:08,820 --> 00:08:09,580
However,

101
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:11,340
next time I see Professor Jiang,

102
00:08:11,340 --> 00:08:13,070
I must criticize him properly.

103
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:15,310
He is still mostly to blame anyway.

104
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,750
No matter how jealous

105
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:18,380
or upset he was,
he shouldn't have mentioned divorce,

106
00:08:18,380 --> 00:08:19,790
let alone kicking you out.

107
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:20,310
Right?

108
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,020
Exactly.

109
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,550
You should learn from me on this.

110
00:08:22,550 --> 00:08:23,900
If my husband dared to do this,

111
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:25,580
I would have beaten him already.

112
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:26,750
I yelled at him.

113
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:28,940
I didn't dare to hit him.

114
00:08:28,940 --> 00:08:30,460
I was afraid he'd sue me
for domestic violence.

115
00:08:30,460 --> 00:08:31,190
Next time,

116
00:08:31,190 --> 00:08:33,070
just give him a shoulder throw.

117
00:08:33,390 --> 00:08:34,580
Throw him on the floor.

118
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:35,309
Pin him down.

119
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:36,789
That'll teach him a lesson
for mentioning divorce.

120
00:08:36,789 --> 00:08:37,789
I'm so mad, sis.

121
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:41,150
I really am.

122
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:45,330
Nothing really happened yesterday.

123
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:48,390
He made me so furious

124
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:50,640
that I barely slept all night.

125
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:53,700
My mental state is terrible now.

126
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:55,510
Then you should catch up on some sleep.

127
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:56,430
I'll head to the unit first.

128
00:08:56,430 --> 00:08:57,560
Don't overthink it.

129
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:04,890
One more thing.

130
00:09:05,740 --> 00:09:07,620
We contacted Zhao Ping's parents.

131
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:08,950
But they refuse to come.

132
00:09:09,340 --> 00:09:10,100
They said

133
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:13,970
they'd pretend
that they never had this son.

134
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:17,620
People.

135
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:29,340
Senior.

136
00:09:32,940 --> 00:09:34,740
I wanted to attend your wedding.

137
00:09:57,820 --> 00:10:00,030
You were kicked out by Jiang Hansheng?

138
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:03,390
Really?

139
00:10:03,980 --> 00:10:05,740
Come on, tell me.

140
00:10:06,620 --> 00:10:07,190
Come on.

141
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,550
What kind of problem is so serious

142
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:10,860
that you two are separated?

143
00:10:10,860 --> 00:10:12,860
Does Jiang Hansheng
have some weird quirks?

144
00:10:12,860 --> 00:10:14,510
If there's something wrong with him,
don't just put up with it.

145
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:16,270
What's that popular phrase now?

146
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,460
Say no to emotional drain.

147
00:10:17,460 --> 00:10:18,270
Jiang Cheng.

148
00:10:18,580 --> 00:10:19,780
What are you here for?

149
00:10:20,030 --> 00:10:21,160
If there's nothing,

150
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:22,700
you can leave now.

151
00:10:22,700 --> 00:10:24,150
Of course there is.

152
00:10:25,220 --> 00:10:25,980
Jin,

153
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:28,340
I think marriage is a lifelong matter.

154
00:10:28,340 --> 00:10:30,190
If it's not working out,
just get a divorce.

155
00:10:30,190 --> 00:10:30,860
Get out!

156
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:36,940
We grew up together, didn't we?

157
00:10:37,270 --> 00:10:38,940
You don't like me now.

158
00:10:38,940 --> 00:10:40,740
I accept that.

159
00:10:41,670 --> 00:10:43,130
Even if we are not a couple,

160
00:10:44,070 --> 00:10:45,790
I can still be considered your brother,
right?

161
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:46,740
That guy Jiang Hansheng,

162
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:48,310
I've always felt something was wrong
with him since we were kids.

163
00:10:48,310 --> 00:10:49,460
Stop talking.

164
00:10:50,510 --> 00:10:52,710
I know exactly what kind of person he is.

165
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:55,930
Don't badmouth him in front of me.

166
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:57,150
Okay, fine.

167
00:10:57,460 --> 00:10:58,520
I'll stop talking.

168
00:10:59,270 --> 00:11:00,940
Officer Jiang, there you are.

169
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:02,340
Everything is ready over there.

170
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:03,470
We can head over now.

171
00:11:04,030 --> 00:11:04,580
Zhou Jin,

172
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,070
Chief Tan heard you were here too.

173
00:11:06,070 --> 00:11:07,390
He asked you to come along.

174
00:11:07,390 --> 00:11:09,270
Okay, I'll get changed and be right there.

175
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:09,790
Okay.

176
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:29,030
[Director Wang Pengze]
[Hansheng is with me.]

177
00:11:36,340 --> 00:11:38,270
You had an argument with your wife,

178
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,740
and now you're here

179
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:41,580
bothering an old man like me?

180
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:42,910
Hurry up and eat.

181
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,460
[Hansheng is with me.]

182
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:57,190
[Mr. Wang, sorry for the trouble.
I had a misunderstanding]

183
00:11:57,190 --> 00:11:57,930
[with Hansheng. I'll go pick him up
when he's in a better mood.]

184
00:12:04,860 --> 00:12:05,700
Please read.

185
00:12:07,310 --> 00:12:07,970
Professor!

186
00:12:08,980 --> 00:12:09,910
How could you...

187
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:15,980
I've got all this gray hair now.

188
00:12:16,550 --> 00:12:17,580
Don't bother me anymore.

189
00:12:16,770 --> 00:12:18,610
[Mr. Wang, sorry for the trouble.
I had a misunderstanding]

190
00:12:18,340 --> 00:12:20,820
It's normal for couples to argue.

191
00:12:18,610 --> 00:12:20,460
[with Hansheng. I'll go pick him up
when he's in a better mood.]

192
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:23,700
Even the tongue and teeth sometimes clash.

193
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:24,830
Whatever happened,

194
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,310
let bygones be bygones.

195
00:12:26,310 --> 00:12:27,980
Don't be so hard on yourself.

196
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:31,410
[Mr. Wang, sorry for the trouble.
I had a misunderstanding
with Hansheng. I'll go pick him up
when he's in a better mood.]

197
00:12:29,070 --> 00:12:31,070
A woman needs to be coaxed.

198
00:12:31,070 --> 00:12:32,620
I'm telling you,
you can't just ignore her.

199
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:35,080
If you ignore her,
her love for you will fade.

200
00:12:35,190 --> 00:12:35,940
Chopsticks.

201
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:43,800
There're just a few lines. Why have you
been reading for so long?

202
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:45,790
Stop reading.

203
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:46,910
Here.

204
00:12:48,100 --> 00:12:49,900
Professor Jiang. Please enjoy.

205
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:53,700
Here.

206
00:13:03,460 --> 00:13:05,430
Look at how pathetic you are.

207
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:14,790
Come in.

208
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:22,030
I've read your psychological evaluation

209
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:23,160
and medical report.

210
00:13:23,270 --> 00:13:24,550
There's no major problem.

211
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:26,150
You can still take some hits.

212
00:13:26,310 --> 00:13:28,170
Then am I allowed to do fieldwork?

213
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:29,900
Wait a little longer.

214
00:13:33,310 --> 00:13:33,940
Chief Tan.

215
00:13:36,620 --> 00:13:37,270
Not bad.

216
00:13:39,190 --> 00:13:40,850
We need you to help us identify

217
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:42,270
the personnel related to Hengyun Logistics

218
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:45,150
and the Kuangshan drug factory.

219
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:46,820
No problem.

220
00:13:53,860 --> 00:13:55,460
Number 1, Number 2, Number 4.

221
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:56,820
The rest are fine.

222
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:58,430
Bring in the next group.

223
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:06,880
Number 4, Number 7.

224
00:14:07,430 --> 00:14:08,760
Bring in the next group.

225
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:15,120
Before Jiang Cheng came back,

226
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:16,860
the profile of Qi Yan

227
00:14:16,190 --> 00:14:17,790
[Qi Yan]

228
00:14:17,070 --> 00:14:18,310
never matched the image the police have

229
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:19,740
of Old Scorpion.

230
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:25,190
[Qi Yan=Old Scorpion?]

231
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:21,460
This led everyone

232
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:22,940
to never suspect

233
00:14:23,430 --> 00:14:25,360
that they could be the same person.

234
00:14:25,580 --> 00:14:26,940
Number 1, 2, and 4.

235
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:28,550
The rest are fine.

236
00:14:29,580 --> 00:14:30,910
Bring in the next group.

237
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:33,570
In Jiang Cheng's previous concept,

238
00:14:33,570 --> 00:14:34,600
[Brother]

239
00:14:33,740 --> 00:14:35,620
Old Scorpion was always an old guy.

240
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,460
[Father???]

241
00:14:36,620 --> 00:14:38,820
It shouldn't have been his assumption,

242
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:40,100
but rather a consensus.

243
00:14:40,100 --> 00:14:41,510
Number 2, 5, 6, and 7.

244
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:44,790
Number 3 and 5.

245
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:47,270
Number 2 and 4.

246
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:49,110
[Drugs] [Killing a Police Officer]

247
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:49,550
Since Qi Yan never showed himself,

248
00:14:49,110 --> 00:14:50,310
[Revenge]

249
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:52,070
naturally,
he needs someone to act on his behalf.

250
00:14:50,310 --> 00:14:51,530
[Qi Yan]

251
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:53,940
This Qi might be

252
00:14:53,940 --> 00:14:55,390
his spokesperson on the surface.

253
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:56,380
[Qi Yan=Old Scorpion?]

254
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:57,980
Qi Yan's history
could be erased completely,

255
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:57,560
[Huaiguang Murder Case—Red Dress, Wrist Slashing, Bow Knot, Oedipus Complex, Misogyny]
[8.17 Case—Drugs, Killing a Police Officer, Sniper, Knife]

256
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:58,740
[Ningyuan, Haizhou Murder Case—
New Red Dress, New Bow Knot, Needle, Protest]

257
00:14:58,550 --> 00:14:59,580
but this Qi's

258
00:14:58,760 --> 00:15:00,710
[Jingang Wharf—Drugs, Killing a Police Officer, Revenge. Kuangshan—Drug Factory]
[Brother? Father?]

259
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:00,730
is less likely to be.

260
00:15:00,730 --> 00:15:01,680
[Oedipus Complex, Anti-Police]
[Qi Zhen, Jian Liang]

261
00:15:01,790 --> 00:15:03,430
Finding a flaw in him

262
00:15:04,190 --> 00:15:05,190
should be easier.

263
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:10,890
Why don't you give Zhou Jin

264
00:15:11,470 --> 00:15:12,400
a call?

265
00:15:14,940 --> 00:15:16,070
I'll call Chief Tan.

266
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:26,990
Chief Tan.

267
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:28,700
We found the car that followed Zhou Jin

268
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:30,100
before her car accident.

269
00:15:30,310 --> 00:15:31,790
It's a car with a fake license plate.

270
00:15:31,790 --> 00:15:33,030
After the accident,

271
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:34,510
the car kept heading toward
the countryside

272
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:36,190
and finally stopped by a ditch.

273
00:15:36,190 --> 00:15:37,150
It's quite remote

274
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:39,350
and there are no surveillance cameras.

275
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:35,880
I've been here before.

276
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:42,100
We hid around here
before we entered Kuangshan.

277
00:16:42,100 --> 00:16:43,190
I remember this smell.

278
00:16:43,190 --> 00:16:45,320
It's a stench with a hint of fishiness.

279
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:48,200
Where were you hiding?

280
00:16:49,190 --> 00:16:50,310
If you look down in this direction,

281
00:16:50,310 --> 00:16:51,620
there should be a village.

282
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:53,860
There's a house with a bamboo fence,

283
00:16:53,860 --> 00:16:55,660
and the walls are painted green.

284
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:57,700
It could easily hide a dozen people.

285
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:58,550
Before entering Kuangshan,

286
00:16:58,550 --> 00:17:00,350
we hid in there for several days.

287
00:17:00,430 --> 00:17:02,030
Although I was blindfolded,

288
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:03,290
I remember this smell.

289
00:17:04,470 --> 00:17:05,380
If you say

290
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:07,380
Qi was in this car,

291
00:17:07,819 --> 00:17:08,750
it's possible.

292
00:17:09,099 --> 00:17:10,829
They have a stronghold nearby.

293
00:17:12,030 --> 00:17:12,579
Lu.

294
00:17:12,900 --> 00:17:13,420
Here.

295
00:17:13,579 --> 00:17:15,339
Find a few people to check it out.

296
00:17:15,339 --> 00:17:15,790
Yes.

297
00:17:17,420 --> 00:17:18,619
You two, come with me.

298
00:17:24,510 --> 00:17:25,510
Yes, Director Lu.

299
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:28,310
If Jiang Cheng's judgment is correct,

300
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:29,790
we need to

301
00:17:29,860 --> 00:17:30,790
act immediately

302
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:32,160
and take them down.

303
00:17:32,380 --> 00:17:33,030
Alright.

304
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:33,940
Let's do this.

305
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:37,020
Give me the action plan
as soon as possible.

306
00:17:37,140 --> 00:17:37,670
Alright.

307
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:42,950
The Provincial Bureau agreed.

308
00:17:42,950 --> 00:17:44,280
Act as soon as possible.

309
00:17:44,470 --> 00:17:44,860
Yes.

310
00:17:45,660 --> 00:17:46,710
You go out and wait.

311
00:17:46,710 --> 00:17:48,140
We have things to discuss.

312
00:17:48,140 --> 00:17:48,950
Yes.

313
00:17:52,230 --> 00:17:53,560
Is there anything else?

314
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:56,510
If we take action,

315
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:57,640
I have two requests.

316
00:17:58,030 --> 00:17:59,560
I hope you can agree to them.

317
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,640
What are your thoughts?

318
00:18:04,070 --> 00:18:04,990
Tell us.

319
00:18:05,470 --> 00:18:06,030
First,

320
00:18:06,140 --> 00:18:07,400
give me an action team.

321
00:18:07,900 --> 00:18:10,340
I want to lead them personally
to make the arrest.

322
00:18:10,340 --> 00:18:11,200
And the second?

323
00:18:11,660 --> 00:18:13,320
I want Zhou Jin to be my deputy.

324
00:18:26,100 --> 00:18:27,550
I understand your feeling

325
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:29,790
of wanting to arrest them yourself.

326
00:18:30,550 --> 00:18:31,480
But Jiang Cheng,

327
00:18:32,540 --> 00:18:35,070
you haven't been
officially reinstated yet.

328
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:37,140
You can at most assist in this operation

329
00:18:37,140 --> 00:18:38,340
as an informed person

330
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:41,410
familiar with the situation.

331
00:18:41,790 --> 00:18:43,140
As for the second request,

332
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:44,340
I can have Zhou Jin

333
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:46,660
be responsible for ensuring your safety.
You'll be in the same team.

334
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:49,590
Once the exact location
of the hideout is confirmed,

335
00:18:50,860 --> 00:18:52,520
your reconnaissance mission

336
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:54,090
will be completed.

337
00:18:59,620 --> 00:19:00,180
Okay.

338
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:01,510
Is that alright?

339
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:03,310
You still don't trust me, do you?

340
00:19:03,380 --> 00:19:04,180
Jiang Cheng!

341
00:19:05,030 --> 00:19:06,490
This is about discipline!

342
00:19:06,710 --> 00:19:08,840
You must get used to following orders.

343
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:13,420
Zhou Jin,

344
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:16,180
the task of protecting him
is assigned to you.

345
00:19:16,180 --> 00:19:17,110
Aside from that,

346
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:19,710
don't cause any unnecessary trouble.

347
00:19:20,100 --> 00:19:20,580
Yes.

348
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:22,930
What about you?

349
00:19:24,270 --> 00:19:24,750
Okay.

350
00:19:25,140 --> 00:19:25,580
Okay.

351
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:27,760
I'll listen to you, Leader.

352
00:19:42,990 --> 00:19:43,230
Come on.

353
00:19:43,230 --> 00:19:45,070
You're working for such a rigid person?

354
00:19:45,070 --> 00:19:47,470
He doesn't even fight
for his subordinates?

355
00:19:47,470 --> 00:19:49,070
Don't speak ill of my mentor.

356
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:50,660
It seems he treats you well.

357
00:19:50,660 --> 00:19:51,920
You quite respect him.

358
00:19:54,620 --> 00:19:55,680
What are you doing?

359
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:01,520
Reporting to Jiang Hansheng?

360
00:20:02,790 --> 00:20:03,620
He doesn't seem

361
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:04,900
to be very confident.

362
00:20:04,900 --> 00:20:05,510
Can he handle

363
00:20:05,510 --> 00:20:07,110
you provoking him like this?

364
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:11,180
Wei asked me if you were reinstated.

365
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:15,350
He's calling.

366
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:17,710
Wei.

367
00:20:18,070 --> 00:20:18,860
Jin,

368
00:20:19,230 --> 00:20:20,490
are you busy right now?

369
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:22,270
Hello.

370
00:20:23,030 --> 00:20:24,380
Seeing you in this uniform

371
00:20:24,380 --> 00:20:25,660
puts my mind at ease.

372
00:20:26,180 --> 00:20:27,840
Yet you never came to visit me.

373
00:20:28,620 --> 00:20:29,820
I've been in meetings every day recently.

374
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:30,620
I'm too busy.

375
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:32,990
What have you guys been busy with lately?

376
00:20:32,990 --> 00:20:35,450
You never reply to my messages
immediately.

377
00:20:35,510 --> 00:20:36,510
Are you that busy?

378
00:20:36,790 --> 00:20:37,580
We are indeed busy.

379
00:20:37,580 --> 00:20:39,380
We also just got out of a meeting.

380
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:40,620
Looks like

381
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:42,310
you were fighting side by side.

382
00:20:42,310 --> 00:20:43,620
I'm happy for you.

383
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:46,950
I also have some good news to tell you.

384
00:20:46,950 --> 00:20:49,070
Do you have any free time
these next few days

385
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:50,270
to come to Jingzhou and attend

386
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:52,400
my son's one-month birthday banquet?

387
00:20:53,030 --> 00:20:55,630
I'll definitely come
if I don't have a mission.

388
00:20:55,660 --> 00:20:57,420
I'm not going.

389
00:20:57,420 --> 00:20:58,510
I can't leave Haizhou.

390
00:20:58,510 --> 00:20:59,790
I'm still in the evaluation period.

391
00:20:59,790 --> 00:21:01,050
Jin will represent me.

392
00:21:01,140 --> 00:21:01,860
Jin,

393
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:04,040
are you bringing your husband?

394
00:21:05,660 --> 00:21:06,990
I'll go ask Hansheng.

395
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,270
Okay.

396
00:21:08,820 --> 00:21:11,510
I happen to have some work-related matters

397
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:13,510
I'd like to consult Professor Jiang about.

398
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:15,710
Then I'll try my best
to get him to go too.

399
00:21:17,710 --> 00:21:19,310
Okay, there's nothing else.

400
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:22,070
Jiang Cheng.

401
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:25,270
How about we find some free time
in the next couple of days

402
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,140
to get together?

403
00:21:26,140 --> 00:21:27,470
He went to the restroom.

404
00:21:29,380 --> 00:21:29,990
Jin,

405
00:21:30,820 --> 00:21:31,790
seeing you again,

406
00:21:31,790 --> 00:21:33,470
he must have mixed feelings.

407
00:21:34,510 --> 00:21:36,510
You should change how you interact.

408
00:21:36,820 --> 00:21:37,880
Don't be too stiff,

409
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:39,070
and don't rush it.

410
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:39,860
I know.

411
00:21:40,670 --> 00:21:41,710
It's hard.

412
00:21:43,180 --> 00:21:43,990
I understand.

413
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:46,530
It will get better.

414
00:21:48,510 --> 00:21:49,110
Oh, right.

415
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:51,750
For your son's one-month birthday banquet,

416
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:53,750
will our former SWAT colleagues go?

417
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,680
Some of them from back then
were restructured,

418
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,140
and some were reassigned.

419
00:21:58,270 --> 00:21:59,870
Now they're all busy people,

420
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:02,310
so they might not make the time to attend.

421
00:22:02,310 --> 00:22:03,110
What's wrong?

422
00:22:04,510 --> 00:22:06,880
I'm thinking they might know my brother.

423
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:10,650
We could probably talk about him
if we see each other.

424
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,550
You're missing you brother?

425
00:22:12,550 --> 00:22:14,680
It must be because of the recent cases.

426
00:22:16,030 --> 00:22:16,680
Wei,

427
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:18,880
do you and your wife

428
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:21,110
still talk about my brother?

429
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:22,880
Rarely.

430
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:25,540
Then does she still remember him?

431
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:26,750
Of course she does.

432
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:29,880
He was her idol back then.

433
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:35,000
Did...

434
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:39,120
Did my brother have any enemies before?

435
00:22:40,830 --> 00:22:42,560
What enemies could Cheng have?

436
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:45,010
Why do you suddenly have this thought?

437
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:46,760
It's nothing.

438
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:48,810
Let's talk when we meet.

439
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:49,750
Okay.

440
00:22:50,550 --> 00:22:51,610
I'm hanging up now.

441
00:23:47,790 --> 00:23:48,520
Jiang Cheng.

442
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:51,400
You're done talking?

443
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:53,960
Why didn't you talk to Wei a bit more?

444
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:56,310
We are grown men.
We don't have that much to say.

445
00:23:56,310 --> 00:23:57,110
Mentor told us

446
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:58,480
to wait for his next instruction

447
00:23:58,480 --> 00:23:59,750
and stand by at all times.

448
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:00,280
Let's go.

449
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:01,240
Okay.

450
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:03,740
You didn't even wipe your face clean.

451
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,000
Look at this.

452
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,790
Is it a new clue?

453
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:16,350
Not really new.

454
00:24:17,590 --> 00:24:19,640
Do you remember the guy who took the fall

455
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:20,880
for the Huaiguang Case?

456
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,830
It's the materials I collected about him.

457
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:23,640
Chen Li?

458
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:24,880
That accountant?

459
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:25,790
Yes.

460
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:28,550
Is there any new progress?

461
00:24:32,590 --> 00:24:34,050
Chen Li's ex-wife is back.

462
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:44,320
Jiang Cheng,

463
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:45,970
we trust your judgment.

464
00:24:46,270 --> 00:24:47,270
Just do your best.

465
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:48,960
You may proceed.

466
00:24:53,830 --> 00:24:55,200
First, drive along this road.

467
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,200
Keep the speed...

468
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:57,160
at 40.

469
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:57,830
Okay.

470
00:25:26,310 --> 00:25:27,550
About 50 meters ahead,

471
00:25:27,550 --> 00:25:29,080
there's a left turn, right?

472
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:30,720
Yes.

473
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:32,000
Turn left.

474
00:25:32,510 --> 00:25:32,960
Okay.

475
00:25:38,670 --> 00:25:40,580
[Pond] [Stinky ditch]

476
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:00,220
Stop here for a second.

477
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:23,550
When we got near here that day,

478
00:26:24,830 --> 00:26:26,310
I smelled burning incense.

479
00:26:26,310 --> 00:26:27,310
Burning incense?

480
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:27,750
Yes.

481
00:26:35,070 --> 00:26:36,070
Command vehicle!

482
00:26:36,070 --> 00:26:37,030
Copy, go ahead.

483
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:38,070
Help me check

484
00:26:38,070 --> 00:26:40,530
if there's any place
to burn incense nearby.

485
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:41,590
For example,

486
00:26:41,830 --> 00:26:42,880
an Earth God temple

487
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,080
or an ancestral hall.

488
00:26:45,590 --> 00:26:47,240
There's a tiny Earth God temple.

489
00:26:47,240 --> 00:26:48,640
Go straight for about 40 meters,

490
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,300
turn right, and you'll see it.

491
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:51,390
Copy that.

492
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:23,590
It's not far now.

493
00:27:23,590 --> 00:27:25,960
Go down this road
for about 500 or 600 meters,

494
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,720
and there's a farmhouse.

495
00:27:27,750 --> 00:27:29,310
It's isolated, with no neighbors.

496
00:27:29,310 --> 00:27:30,790
It's the one I told you about yesterday,

497
00:27:30,790 --> 00:27:32,550
the small yard with the bamboo fence.

498
00:27:32,550 --> 00:27:34,080
Wait a minute. Let me check.

499
00:27:40,110 --> 00:27:40,720
Found it.

500
00:27:41,350 --> 00:27:42,510
Send it to the action team.

501
00:27:42,510 --> 00:27:43,000
Yes.

502
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:45,160
Well done, Jiang Cheng.

503
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:46,620
Your mission is complete.

504
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:13,790
Are there any extra walkie-talkies
in the car?

505
00:28:13,790 --> 00:28:14,830
Yes.

506
00:28:15,110 --> 00:28:16,840
Bring one over. Mine is broken.

507
00:28:17,550 --> 00:28:18,400
Coming.

508
00:28:26,010 --> 00:28:28,600
[Police]

509
00:28:42,800 --> 00:28:44,120
[SWAT]

510
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:46,400
Report.

511
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:48,110
We have surrounded the target courtyard,

512
00:28:48,110 --> 00:28:49,880
but there are 3 entrances
at the front and back.

513
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:51,750
We cannot further investigate
the situation inside.

514
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:52,880
Please give orders.

515
00:28:55,550 --> 00:28:56,310
Take action.

516
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:57,270
Yes.

517
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:10,320
I know what you're thinking.

518
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,400
But it's the rule.

519
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:19,160
No need to remind me.

520
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:21,550
I understand.

521
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:24,620
I'm just assisting with the investigation.

522
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:41,620
Godfather,

523
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:42,270
please,

524
00:29:42,440 --> 00:29:43,770
give me one last chance.

525
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:45,590
No wonder you kept making mistakes

526
00:29:45,590 --> 00:29:48,070
and bringing me bad luck
for the past year and a half.

527
00:29:48,070 --> 00:29:49,680
Turns out you're a mole.

528
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:01,510
Well...

529
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,720
Yao Weihai...

530
00:30:05,350 --> 00:30:06,680
I'll leave him to you.

531
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:07,690
Understood.

532
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,460
Thanks for your hard work.

533
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,030
Alright.

534
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:15,170
The mole has been taken care of.

535
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:17,250
And my mission is complete.

536
00:30:17,790 --> 00:30:18,960
Next step...

537
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:20,790
Jiang Cheng,

538
00:30:21,750 --> 00:30:22,960
prove yourself.

539
00:30:26,110 --> 00:30:26,960
I get it.

540
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:28,850
A pledge of loyalty.

541
00:30:50,590 --> 00:30:51,790
At a 45-degree angle.

542
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:53,960
Against the head.

543
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:09,790
You used to be a cop.

544
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:12,590
Do you dare to kill one?

545
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:15,070
Why wouldn't I dare?

546
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:18,640
Then do it.

547
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:21,920
The sun is almost up.

548
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:33,960
Before his last mission,

549
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:37,200
he asked me to get him

550
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:38,660
one of those

551
00:31:38,790 --> 00:31:40,440
little cyanide capsules.

552
00:31:41,590 --> 00:31:43,520
He said the mission was dangerous,

553
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:45,660
and it might come in handy.

554
00:31:58,110 --> 00:31:59,110
No matter how hard

555
00:31:59,720 --> 00:32:00,780
or dangerous it is,

556
00:32:01,750 --> 00:32:02,410
I accept it.

557
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:30,000
Jiang Cheng,

558
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:32,340
you really didn't let me down.

559
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:35,200
How could I let you pull the trigger?

560
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:37,040
After all, you saved my life.

561
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,920
Didn't you want to see Old Scorpion?

562
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:48,480
You'll see him soon.

563
00:33:06,550 --> 00:33:07,310
Jiang Cheng.

564
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:11,160
What's wrong?

565
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:18,400
Jin,

566
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:21,400
sometimes living is harder than dying.

567
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:22,510
You know?

568
00:33:25,270 --> 00:33:27,640
Bearing all the trust alone,

569
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:29,440
yet being unable to do anything.

570
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:34,200
Whenever I think of Yao's last moments,

571
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:37,480
and that Meng Junfeng died for me,

572
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:40,440
I feel like even taking a breath

573
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:42,880
is wrong.

574
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:45,350
No.

575
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,880
It's not like that.

576
00:33:53,510 --> 00:33:54,200
Jin,

577
00:33:55,830 --> 00:33:57,560
I must get this revenge myself.

578
00:33:58,310 --> 00:34:00,170
If I don't go and atone for my sins,

579
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:03,000
I will never forgive myself.

580
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:13,030
Jin, untie me!

581
00:34:13,670 --> 00:34:14,360
Jin!

582
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:15,800
Didn't you hear what I said?

583
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:16,880
If I don't get this revenge,

584
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:18,320
I won't be at peace!

585
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:19,400
Shut up!

586
00:34:20,030 --> 00:34:21,590
If you do something stupid again,

587
00:34:21,590 --> 00:34:23,110
I will never forgive you!

588
00:34:31,190 --> 00:34:32,920
I've already lost one brother.

589
00:34:36,760 --> 00:34:38,760
I can't lose another family member.

590
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:59,440
Why are you always so mean to me?

591
00:35:00,110 --> 00:35:02,440
Are you like this with Jiang Hansheng too?

592
00:35:04,710 --> 00:35:05,970
None of your business.

593
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:25,480
Professor Jiang.

594
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:28,480
Zhou Jin participated in
today's capture operation?

595
00:35:28,590 --> 00:35:29,520
How did you know?

596
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:32,500
I'll be there soon.

597
00:35:32,670 --> 00:35:34,070
Are you going to the scene?

598
00:35:34,070 --> 00:35:35,000
Qi Yan knows her.

599
00:35:35,630 --> 00:35:36,890
I'm worried about her.

600
00:35:37,550 --> 00:35:39,280
You don't need to worry too much.

601
00:35:39,280 --> 00:35:41,110
Zhou Jin is just
in the Surveillance team this time.

602
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:42,760
She's not directly participating
in the operation.

603
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:43,670
She should be

604
00:35:43,960 --> 00:35:44,960
very safe now.

605
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:48,090
I need to see with my own eyes
that she's safe.

606
00:35:54,710 --> 00:35:55,590
Command vehicle.

607
00:35:55,590 --> 00:35:56,630
The scene is basically under control.

608
00:35:56,630 --> 00:35:58,070
But we didn't see the prime suspect.

609
00:35:58,070 --> 00:35:59,150
Please pay attention to the perimeter.

610
00:35:59,150 --> 00:36:00,760
Maybe the prime suspect has escaped

611
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:01,880
from a blind spot.

612
00:36:04,150 --> 00:36:05,610
Old Scorpion isn't there?

613
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,150
Qi Yan,

614
00:36:07,150 --> 00:36:07,670
Qi,

615
00:36:07,670 --> 00:36:08,230
and Qiu Ye—

616
00:36:08,230 --> 00:36:09,360
none of them is here.

617
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:11,280
Attention,
perimeter reconnaissance vehicles.

618
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:13,230
See if any suspicious persons escaped.

619
00:36:13,230 --> 00:36:14,800
The prime suspect is still at large.

620
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,260
No traces have been found.

621
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:17,590
Copy that.

622
00:36:25,550 --> 00:36:26,190
Jin,

623
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:27,030
untie me.

624
00:36:27,670 --> 00:36:28,230
Jin.

625
00:36:28,630 --> 00:36:30,230
Hurry! Unlock my handcuffs!

626
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:30,960
Jin!

627
00:36:31,190 --> 00:36:31,840
Jin!

628
00:36:32,230 --> 00:36:33,840
Don't go alone, Jin!

629
00:36:35,710 --> 00:36:36,280
Jin!

630
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:37,510
Jin!

631
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,920
Chief Tan, suspects found here.

632
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:44,760
Requesting backup.

633
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,050
[Police]

634
00:36:46,110 --> 00:36:47,150
Stop! Don't run!

635
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,550
Two men, armed.

636
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:02,600
They got into a black sedan.

637
00:37:08,590 --> 00:37:09,440
Black Chevrolet,

638
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:10,280
65K51.

639
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:14,840
Don't be scared!

640
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:16,240
Drive straight through!

641
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:38,390
Hold on tight!

642
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:42,040
Zhou Jin.

643
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:44,000
Hansheng and I are driving to chase them.

644
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,190
They are in our sight,

645
00:37:45,190 --> 00:37:46,510
heading down the mountain road.

646
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:47,670
Stay on the suspects.

647
00:37:47,670 --> 00:37:48,800
Backup is on the way.

648
00:38:31,550 --> 00:38:32,280
Stop the car!

649
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,190
Stop resisting!

650
00:38:33,190 --> 00:38:33,840
Hit him!

651
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:35,550
Hit him!

652
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:39,870
Hold on tight.

653
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:50,010
Floor the gas pedal!

654
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,960
Floor it!

655
00:38:57,230 --> 00:38:58,890
I guess we've made up now, huh?

656
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:06,880
Stop the car!

657
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:36,210
Stop the car!

658
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,160
Don't turn the wheel!

659
00:39:53,630 --> 00:39:54,960
Let's all die together!

660
00:41:14,630 --> 00:41:15,400
Zhou Jin...

661
00:41:39,670 --> 00:41:40,920
-Junior!
-Zhou!

662
00:41:41,150 --> 00:41:41,760
Zhou!

663
00:41:42,030 --> 00:41:43,320
Open the door! Open it!

664
00:41:44,190 --> 00:41:45,280
Junior, wake up!

665
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:46,280
Zhou, wake up!

666
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:47,690
Pull harder!

667
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:51,800
Zhou!

668
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:55,150
Junior, wake up!

669
00:41:55,150 --> 00:41:55,960
Zhou, wake up.

670
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:56,880
Junior, wake up!

671
00:41:56,880 --> 00:41:58,480
I will never nag you again, Junior!

672
00:41:58,480 --> 00:41:59,810
-Zhou.
-Junior Sister!

673
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:01,800
Zhou?

674
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:03,200
Junior, are you okay?

675
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:04,630
How do you feel?

676
00:42:05,590 --> 00:42:06,320
How do you feel?

677
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:07,070
How do you feel?

678
00:42:07,070 --> 00:42:07,880
I'm fine.

679
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:09,190
Are you alright?

680
00:42:09,190 --> 00:42:10,990
I-I'll get you some water, okay?

681
00:42:11,230 --> 00:42:12,670
-Come on.
-Be careful.

682
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:17,520
I'm glad you're okay.

683
00:42:17,630 --> 00:42:20,090
Wan,
what's the situation at the scene like?

684
00:42:20,400 --> 00:42:21,510
Qi has been arrested.

685
00:42:21,510 --> 00:42:23,040
The scene is under control.

686
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:24,320
But there are people injured.

687
00:42:24,320 --> 00:42:25,720
We need medical support.

688
00:42:27,880 --> 00:42:29,030
Medical team! Medical team!
